# 1. 核心策略：所有文件默认按文本处理，统一使用 LF
* text=auto eol=lf

# 2. 显式定义文本文件类型（确保脚本、配置、标记语言等不被误判）
*.sh text eol=lf
*.py text eol=lf
*.js text eol=lf
*.ts text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
*.xml text eol=lf
*.html text eol=lf
*.css text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.txt text eol=lf
*.gitignore text eol=lf
*.gitattributes text eol=lf
*.dockerignore text eol=lf
*.env text eol=lf

# 3. 严格定义二进制文件（防止 Git 尝试转换或 diff）
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.bmp binary
*.tiff binary
*.ico binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
*.tar binary
*.gz binary
*.7z binary
*.rar binary
*.exe binary
*.dll binary
*.so binary
*.dylib binary
*.jar binary
*.war binary
*.class binary

# 4. 特殊处理：生成的文件或日志（不进行换行符转换，避免干扰构建）
*.log binary
*.min.js binary
*.min.css binary